@startuml
title YPS PushMoney - Y Repo / S Repo Split

actor Caller
participant "Y Repo" as Y
database "Y Repo DB" as YDB
participant "Printer" as Printer
participant "Publisher" as Pub
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "S Repo" as S
database "S Repo DB" as SDB

Caller -> Y: pushMoney(request)
Y -> Y: validate + prepare draft sale
Y -> YDB: save draft + outbox
Y -> Printer: print voucher
Y --> Caller: return success

Pub -> YDB: read NEW outbox
Pub -> MQ: publish event
Pub -> YDB: mark SENT

MQ -> S: consume event
S -> SDB: save sale_transaction
S -> SDB: save commission
S -> SDB: save print/audit records
@enduml